    <item>
      <title>伊曼纽尔称市场通常喜欢统一的政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/markets-usually-like-unified-governments-emanuel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Evercore ISI 高级董事总经理朱利安·伊曼纽尔 (Julian Emanuel) 表示，当政府统一时，股市通常会上涨，因为他们往往会花更多的钱。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/markets-usually-like-unified-governments-emanuel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:58:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
