      <title>供应增加、需求疲软加剧悲观情绪，油价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在利比亚达成恢复石油供应的协议后，交易员们的注意力又重新转移到对全球原油需求低迷的担忧上，油价随之暴跌，抹去了今年的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 23:26:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
